- **[DELETE]** [User.js](file:///c:/Users/bibha/Desktop/sahayog-sarthi/backend/src/models/User.js)
- **[DELETE]** [Worker.js](file:///c:/Users/bibha/Desktop/sahayog-sarthi/backend/src/models/Worker.js)
