- **`MongoPaymentRepository.js`**
  - Change: `import Payment from '../../../../../models/Payment.js';` ➔ `import Payment from '../../../../payment/infrastructure/persistence/schemas/PaymentSchema.js';`
  - Change: `import Booking from '../../../../../models/Booking.js';` ➔ `import Booking from '../../../../booking/infrastructure/persistence/schemas/BookingSchema.js';`
